Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI

Class ClientIsland

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI.ClientIsland
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ClientIsland extends Object implements Serializable
Class ClientIsland holds basic information about an Island state in order to render its content through CLI and GUI interfaces. It carries information about towers, student tiles and bans placed on it. It also allows verifying whether Mother Nature is placed on it or not.
